    "It was ensured that the first row of P were all nonnegative values, achieved by multiplying the entire corresponding column by -1 if the first-row entry was negative.",
    "This paper assumes that the weights wi sum to 1.",
    "By multiplying these weights by the authors' result Xi j in the section \"Back to Initial Placement\", this makes w'X j the weighted average of supplier changes from one time period to the next.",
    "Alternatively, Xi j is the percentage change in the aggregate supplier quantity multiplied by each weight wi.",
    "This translates to calculating N+1 different scenarios ΔQi j = wiXi j (S/100) for j = 1,…,N+1 and for S = Q1 j + … + QN j."
